# Environment Variables Setup

## MongoDB Configuration
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://root:root@aerolanduserdb.uojig88.mongodb.net/
MONGODB_DB=aeroland

## Site Configuration
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://your-vercel-app.vercel.app
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=http://localhost:3000
```

## Instructions for Vercel Deployment

1. Go to Vercel Project Settings
2. Navigate to Environment Variables
3. Add the following variables:
   - `MONGODB_URI`: MongoDB Atlas connection string
   - `MONGODB_DB`: aeroland (or your database name)
   - `NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL`: Your Vercel production URL

Make sure the MongoDB Atlas IP whitelist includes Vercel IPs or set it to allow all IPs (0.0.0.0/0) for development.
